#: hello/templates/hello/about.html:11 hello/templates/hello/home.html:22
msgid "What Are Rock Cannons?"
msgstr "Beth Yw Canonau Cerrig?"

#: hello/templates/hello/about.html:13
msgid ""
"Rock cannons were used in the 18th and 19th centuries to create loud sounds "
"that scared birds away from crops. They were often made from old cannons or "
"large metal pipes and fired with gunpowder. The blast helped farmers protect "
"their harvests."
msgstr ""
"Defnyddiwyd canonau cerrig yn y 18fed a'r 19eg ganrif i greu synau uchel "
"a ddychrynai adar oddi wrth gnydau. Fe'u gwnaed yn aml o hen ganonau neu "
"bib metel mawr ac fe'u taniwyd a phowdwr gwn. Helpodd y ffrwydrad ffermwyr "
"i ddiogelu eu cynhaeaf."

#: hello/templates/hello/about.html:16
msgid ""
"Today, rock cannons remain an important part of local heritage. In many "
"places they are now fired during festivals and community events, where they "
"represent history, identity, and tradition."
msgstr ""
"Heddiw, mae canonau cerrig yn parhau i fod yn rhan bwysig o dreftadaeth "
"leol. Mewn llawer o leoedd fe'u taniwyd bellach yn ystod gwyliau a "
"digwyddiadau cymunedol, lle maent yn cynrychioli hanes, hunaniaeth a "
"thraddodiad."

#: hello/templates/hello/about.html:21
msgid "Rock Cannon in landscape"
msgstr "Canon Carreg mewn tirwedd"

#: hello/templates/hello/about.html:25
msgid "Historic rock cannon site"
msgstr "Safle canon carreg hanesyddol"

#: hello/templates/hello/about.html:29
msgid "Preserving Their History"
msgstr "Cadw eu Hanes"

#: hello/templates/hello/about.html:31
msgid ""
"Preserving the history of rock cannons helps us understand the creativity "
"and resilience of farming communities. Their story connects people to the "
"landscape, local memory, and traditions passed down through generations."
msgstr ""
"Mae cadw hanes canonau cerrig yn ein helpu i ddeall creadigrwydd a "
"gwydnwch cymunedau ffermio. Mae eu stori yn cysylltu pobl a'r dirwedd, "
"y cof lleol, a thraddodiadau a basiwyd i lawr drwy genedlaethau."

#: hello/templates/hello/about.html:34
msgid ""
"Keeping these sites visible and documented also supports education and "
"tourism, helping more people discover this unique part of Welsh heritage."
msgstr ""
"Mae cadw'r safleoedd hyn yn weladwy ac wedi'u dogfennu hefyd yn cefnogi "
"addysg a thwristiaeth, gan helpu mwy o bobl i ddarganfod y rhan unigryw "
"hon o dreftadaeth Cymru."

